&lt;b&gt;Title:&lt;/b&gt; A Visit To Thyatira: Should You Attend A Church That Has Unbiblical Worship/Doctrine?&lt;BR&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Subtitle:&lt;/b&gt; Biblical Worship&lt;BR&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Speaker:&lt;/b&gt; W. J. Mencarow&lt;BR&gt;
