<item>
	<title>SERMON: The Destruction of Babylon Is The Liberation Of The Nations</title>
	<pubDate>Sat, 1 Aug 2009 16:48 GMT</pubDate>
	<link>http://www.sermonaudio.com/sermoninfo.asp?SID=81091144547</link>
